Harry Lillis Crosby (Tacoma, United States, Mee 3, 1903-Alcobendas, Spain, Ọktọba 14, 1977), onye akpọrọ akpọrọ Bing Crosby, bụ onye America na-agụ egwú (crooner) na onye na-eme ihe nkiri na ọkara ọrụ narị afọ. Kpakpando kpakpando mbụ, Bing Crosby bụ onye kacha ere ma na-eme nke ọma na egwu egwu na narị afọ nke 20 n'ụwa niile.
